<br>
For a melee character, a Fungus Scale Tunic is an item that can be bought for (I paid) 80k that will greatly reduce downtime, starting at level 1. <br>
<br>
If I rerolled a caster, could I sell the fungi and replace it with anything that will be the equal to the effect on a melee in regards to reducing downtime, other than purchasing 8000 KEI castings?  I know there are things like Earing of Solstic that give Flowing Thought 1, but is that even equal to a breeze? Or is the only middle ground to start a shaman and keep the fungi? Or is there melee ability actually completely crappy and they are still a caster more than anything else?<br>
<br>
